name: Market Segmenter
tagline: Market Segmenter web app based on CitySDK
body:
### Welcome to Market Segmenter

This is a web app, based on [CitySDK](http://uscensusbureau.github.io/citysdk/), that was built in one day by the [Specialty Biz](https://github.com/specialtybiz/) team during the [National Day of Civic Hacking](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A_fT6T3lQqE) in Washington DC.

### Support or Contact

Having trouble with this app? Check out our [issues](https://github.com/specialtybiz/marketsegmenter/issues) page and weâ€™ll help you sort it out.
